BDB Urges German Lawmakers to Back Euro-Rescue Package

-- B y   K a r i n   M a t u s s e k
-- 
2011-09-25T13:10:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-25/bdb-urges-german-lawmakers-to-back-euro-rescue-package.html
The BDB German Banking Association
has called upon lawmakers to back revised measures for the euro
rescue fund, scheduled to go to vote this week, with a “strong
majority.” The German parliaments must stand by the euro to
avoid a failure of the common currency zone, the BDB said in an
e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Karin Matussek at 
 kmatussek@bloomberg.net  